A function that is triggered on a schedule.
Schedule field usees cron format for the values:
 * - wildcard
* / n - every n seconds/minutes/hours
a-b range of values between a and b
a,b,c discreet values a,b,c (can be combined w/ range)
 @property {boolean} enabled 
 @property {function} function 
 @property {path} key 
 @property {datetime} last_execution 
 @property {composite} schedule
